    public class MilStdSymbol
extends mil.emp3.api.abstracts.Feature
implements org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoMilSymbol
    This class encapsulates a GeoMilSymbol. It provides additional functionality.

      • MilStdSymbol

        public MilStdSymbol(org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoMilSymbol oRenderable)
             throws EMP_Exception
        This constructor creates MilStdSymbol and encapsulates the IGeoMilSymbol object provided. If the standard version is not set, it is set to the default value. If the modifiers are null it is set to an empty modifier list.
        Parameters:
        oRenderable - an object that implements the IGeoMilSymbol interface.
        Throws:
        EMP_Exception - This exception is raised if the geo renderable provided has an invalid symbol code.

        public void setIconScale(double dScale)
